{"tid":1986982,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"郭榮鏗主持內會並繼續處理民主派議員提出議案","createTime":"2020-04-24T07:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T08:13:52.000Z","uid":149978,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9bcf8a2deea9565e67586839c93d389dc6c1090","tid":1986982,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"立法會內務委員會舉行第16次會議，仍未選出正副主席。<br />\n<br />\n會議期間，主持會議的公民黨法律界議員郭榮鏗處理民主派議員的議案，包括要求立法會秘書長陳維安出席會議，回應立法會保安事宜。多名建制派議員提出規程問題，質疑郭榮鏗無權處理內會正副主席選舉以外的事宜。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗表示，有權處理與內會正副主席選舉相關的動議。在表決之前，建制派召集人廖長江表示，代表建制派聲明，即使投票表態，亦不代表承認郭榮鏗有權力處理相關議案，議案最終在建制派反對下否決。<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗隨後繼續處理其他民主派議員的議案，包括要求陳維安交代警方去年多次進入立法會大樓執法的事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522518-20200424.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522518-20200424.htm&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=7631ece6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522518-20200424.htm&h=a6582383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522518-20200424.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1fe8054f627916bd243413709310ef2db199c83e","tid":1986982,"uid":233193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"鏗鏗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106805a5868130ae3203642fd0670da351f73f33","tid":1986982,"uid":173844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"加油啊 撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d956a8731e55e568f2503b99f4d0f1783c9b51d","tid":1986982,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"106805a5868130ae3203642fd06